**SUSTAINABLE TECHNOLOGY ADOPTION SCORE: 72/100**

Technology Adoption: 18/25  
Innovation Leadership: 18/25  
Measurable Impact: 17/25  
Future Strategy: 11/15  
Industry Position: 8/10

Overall Assessment: Howmet Aerospace is a strong mid‑to‑upper performer on sustainable technologies. The company has deployed several practical, industry‑relevant low‑carbon technologies at scale (energy‑efficiency projects, rooftop solar on major facilities, and lower‑CO2 product variants such as the Green Concept Wheel), supports lightweighting materials and propulsion improvements with a sizable patent and R&D base, and has delivered documented Scope 1 & 2 emissions reductions. It is not yet a clear industry “disrupter” driving a paradigm shift (Scope 3 goals and radical proprietary climate tech are still emerging), but it shows credible innovation leadership and measurable operational impact with a clear near‑term roadmap.

Summary of findings and justification by research area

Technology Adoption (18/25) — findings and evidence
- Energy efficiency and operational projects: Howmet implemented >40 projects in 2022 and identified 100+ projects (investments approved across several years) to reduce energy use and emissions; company reports ~300 million MJ annual energy savings from projects and ~95,600 tCO2e avoided from production/process improvements in recent reporting. These efforts drove a 13.7% intensity improvement and contributed materially to GHG reduction targets. [howmet (id 0-5)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEMJtDJTFRBnpRPUfWlNNkb4S8kEVVmmEJnTBdq_7KWJWwwm4GLPBaeUBO3RDWkMzjyqIRPafPIhxtHJbXtOSwp8nwkbm0rI0XoelMKUyx5P31JwZVuN5lhk5H75PqAcbcBeuMEdp3MZ8lkSoQmQLTZgeqzLPHGZm1NvjzErfzQq3sTsOnPx4OeQ7KRIYihUjFAkl8U8h02SareiGm3S2zIrN2svGbAdg==) [howmet (id 1-2)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkmJ70iPFAo6C6ukUbRQJcKKaJ86hoYL3z75KLs-n8rDTZPaqXzaX8dB7PD-ASztY0WvYSDPXM45IYyDf_PeAq9T_zpNpIzsbU3oCYCl-ToxXKHxjGIXXPrf7Q350oRZ2sdeFxPS6TGXQ__eXsTQzvAgE07DA08957CBryx4Tu_dmt-pKGCXz0iw5ddISnpBHQSryow5t04rrMA8d0ED89dtXRMN40eIk=) [howmet (id 2-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECDl0c7V8v-ECp7CBjyghvg5IWiFB1IdNR3IMYtep_iZoctmssbXOqoTvKvAaKWzjbXEs9MSg6peFMnHk4bm3oqQg4UIIyaDZhGNBoVJe20V4s7cu2JChfaKw5qH0Yzg4dJdYDiz1Yd8wfY_eIIdMIFbiDo8m2f-IMZpBpprNu7HWmC5zdWKC86WiX9FukwPKWNVLn9gCcN6z1P3kO3UthqS12-rZtWw=) [howmet (id 2-3)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEgBS7dDo2Ns44QI39ksCwWTkTSJmzgHXafUKvghi51wwor5IXTmiRzGTI1A5L75Nn3RCc7xL-XmeqwWcCEuZXXuDOzFXJMGroii-IoFsQ3ZpAAz9tKwuxuBVda8SxWZgbCa4pmDnNSjTnBxo7jRByTodLc4hJYUOSUAstqyiYsdyPCLlv0xRYP) [dcfmodeling (id 1-7)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH4TXulx7BuXg_pycv-cEp4v72iDNIpLvT4C-Nl_oJt2f9hkfmYAnVOklZzJV7szOpnG0bc99BRHAgzBk427ii8TRh2ZxoKf4LjW8zbsUhRuhMSKxDwOQsBQbJWSk0aV0VQ_LZ8m2GMyE_pfR4mJe4xKZw=).
- Onsite renewables: Examples of facility solar installations include the Fastening Systems facility in Casablanca (rooftop solar supplying ~25–37% of site energy; ≈900 MWh/year; ≈400 tCO2e saved annually) and Exeter, U.K. (≈1,025 panels ≈20% of building electricity). Companywide renewable electricity in 2024 was ~10.6% of electricity. [howmet (id 3-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFC6OfspWZm5G_2blho7AXecH0yFmXSjCZVTB9fY6r3dJJ8k4Uh51PNsXvWlTCR38Y8qo8DZEoxLZUGaS-MFNi1Rnbnu8WT4zyyel2zU2eGSW0HsIBX_7w0D-qA3odTM5bmu-WBkEqlqu4BH1OlboZBH1HW_VGKgziq4mifuQ3cSJd7U0iy19fBZAM69Dle9zuT5VYIUgFneGZYhSUWZrPJR8o8rP7NmQs=) [howmet (id 3-7)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE3MlwmuPVRzBIOv1hLna-c7HmrCPKQ_VHxLMHkjPhnw_UHsUDT-epuqCKj5HUMwLxaxAKmjs3NXfEmbhnmXGVbgv1r_YcTo6Z1tdDwQzzgMN2H5I8qEGox-mofcji-kvuhVBSKavsjUAoIshZmfGEKJp8EwXS0j5and4AWe54cfw6Caa0ihv_w-IRif6AMmR-yU7DVQxEw75pxfVPUjCeUpfw3HZ5bw52cROPkW3A=) [howmet (id 2-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECDl0c7V8v-ECp7CBjyghvg5IWiFB1IdNR3IMYtep_iZoctmssbXOqoTvKvAaKWzjbXEs9MSg6peFMnHk4bm3oqQg4UIIyaDZhGNBoVJe20V4s7cu2JChfaKw5qH0Yzg4dJdYDiz1Yd8wfY_eIIdMIFbiDo8m2f-IMZpBpprNu7HWmC5zdWKC86WiX9FukwPKWNVLn9gCcN6z1P3kO3UthqS12-rZtWw=).
- Sustainable products & lightweighting: Howmet advances materials (titanium aluminide alloys, advanced multi‑material components) and forged aluminum wheels that reduce vehicle/engine weight and fuel use — e.g., titanium aluminide reducing component weight 25–30% with fuel efficiency uplift; forged aluminum wheels reduce truck emissions >10% vs steel. The 2024 Green Concept Wheel claims ~80% lower CO2e in manufacture vs standard wheels. [ainvest (id 1-5)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH0MIcmBEk7Sb-mny7VIMBrPkiAwH2autURUMwzd_inKg85Yz2HPrN8wYp26muavbwwGiUdDmrBo-EZf3l6YGquSK5Nxvqg42_sDBX7watx6T71iA3vfTchCV6ymvCUCHD95p7q0kfvXTcYEz1rAqeXriWgOqXygDrEE943p0eM9XZ0-oKekQ_HveHQ7tMirIws_bjCz2fdc0LG0Pk=) [howmet (id 3-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFC6OfspWZm5G_2blho7AXecH0yFmXSjCZVTB9fY6r3dJJ8k4Uh51PNsXvWlTCR38Y8qo8DZEoxLZUGaS-MFNi1Rnbnu8WT4zyyel2zU2eGSW0HsIBX_7w0D-qA3odTM5bmu-WBkEqlqu4BH1OlboZBH1HW_VGKgziq4mifuQ3cSJd7U0iy19fBZAM69Dle9zuT5VYIUgFneGZYhSUWZrPJR8o8rP7NmQs=) [howmet (id 2-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECDl0c7V8v-ECp7CBjyghvg5IWiFB1IdNR3IMYtep_iZoctmssbXOqoTvKvAaKWzjbXEs9MSg6peFMnHk4bm3oqQg4UIIyaDZhGNBoVJe20V4s7cu2JChfaKw5qH0Yzg4dJdYDiz1Yd8wfY_eIIdMIFbiDo8m2f-IMZpBpprNu7HWmC5zdWKC86WiX9FukwPKWNVLn9gCcN6z1P3kO3UthqS12-rZtWw=).
- Digital/AI: Howmet is embedding machine learning for predictive maintenance, quality control and has consolidated ERP/data infrastructure to enable AI-driven optimization (operational efficiency and energy management). [ainvest (id 1-6)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQENtXABKCzeEZpkYR_MBvDR_2Bg1ksmnWKSQkVu9blTF7HexhM1qdFK7TDz5dj82p1IgTO3oaIH0y5lIE_nt43nQR-Fqw46BY4RpL0O7zMqdAVa5yryYDS5k-gbSH-k6iYqrSL3Rq2ta3Qyhrxgt-UZWgz-nn_8ScUSi9qLIUE1juxJxl2wqvpOsbNZstHpS-QL6wiGD6ONs3twP1uDjpvO_LYyXTc_X3l6jb3oRQ==) [ainvest (id 1-8)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFFJxHPANqIaXa8e8cyWBpVD1fcniaISEkaIEVVFQTCizFZqWSuDp4yLQarWmO6dX3gSWBGvaluFv2ShobSt7MErFXAzeVeQD417NdLEKWV9yKU6l1ud-Zw4SBnzL77UTTTDEB7IaKfsHOjYKaSvYDg-IGLmWTaAn_xBMqz5lxG8WSKduvkW5xoRkbNHZVAp9QdOl2SdRBb7sTfY0cVpHGopmA73eps1Kctnw==).

Why 18/25: Howmet has deployed multiple meaningful sustainable technologies across operations and product lines (energy efficiency, onsite solar, lightweight materials, lower‑CO2 product variants). This aligns with “several innovative technologies deployed with significant operational integration.” The company is not given the top bracket because truly breakthrough, firm‑owned climate technologies (e.g., large‑scale proprietary low‑carbon energy systems or broad commercial rollouts across the whole footprint) are not yet apparent.

Innovation Leadership (18/25) — findings and evidence
- Patent and R&D scale: Howmet reports ~1,170 granted/pending patents and substantial R&D investment (e.g., reported R&D of ~$143M in 2024 and prior significant propulsion R&D spending including ~$259M referenced for 2022). The portfolio includes propulsion‑system and materials patents that directly enable fuel efficiency gains. [howmet (id 4-4)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHKfjN68z_hmnHoN2zC7XF-oLcz5Q9eH9W-2zEUn3XgduPqpfhePC0l0wD0l1-vA7vKc4aaM0APdmTXti792toSrHG3QSdnrZIXOXF55OzRKkIdzNk-iWUzNpAqJvVTfHfqzp8N5RzwR0J4pxeTCZuV9E19TizMe_SB6R7ND9RM2fTJ5DWcRGT9UqShTRfk8w==) [dcfmodeling (id 1-7)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH4TXulx7BuXg_pycv-cEp4v72iDNIpLvT4C-Nl_oJt2f9hkfmYAnVOklZzJV7szOpnG0bc99BRHAgzBk427ii8TRh2ZxoKf4LjW8zbsUhRuhMSKxDwOQsBQbJWSk0aV0VQ_LZ8m2GMyE_pfR4mJe4xKZw=) [ainvest (id 4-9)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEJmitzyXZlC4fPBmIoNOwOUNgXvJRsNJSFbiCacHn0p4xtwrsvbpXm6bVx3RsTtODDHc0_oYFBFLAZboTcJYc6Yn6z91eykG4HqfzZFRh5X1Vh1_3wie_kQGGFLsvIMqh59950RRsJ2p9Jl5rFIP3Ttvoov9kdj2nV75gBycReac9IHmGHB0GjdQaQqKh37UlkpZXsB1CmTP3SfHc=).
- Targeted R&D & product innovation: Howmet invests in technologies supporting higher‑efficiency engines (airfoils, materials that can run hotter/under higher pressures), is active on enabling SAF and hydrogen engine concepts, and introduced the Green Concept Wheel (2024). [howmet (id 1-2)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkmJ70iPFAo6C6ukUbRQJcKKaJ86hoYL3z75KLs-n8rDTZPaqXzaX8dB7PD-ASztY0WvYSDPXM45IYyDf_PeAq9T_zpNpIzsbU3oCYCl-ToxXKHxjGIXXPrf7Q350oRZ2sdeFxPS6TGXQ__eXsTQzvAgE07DA08957CBryx4Tu_dmt-pKGCXz0iw5ddISnpBHQSryow5t04rrMA8d0ED89dtXRMN40eIk=) [howmet (id 4-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF-sMSGUwyPFZCUZp8KWlkybyk_YaX7LItH3yCRpkz3LCvBbLs3u-V3142DqRndrPganHCJP8y5rX4alUgyK5F5KTwZz2AveWkPzOiTNcOTgekykiLPMnG09Sny5rjAkMqH35YzS7RYR0Wyl7agBLEXvCs933NFJ4ig_y7imboEFk9Tn1ts1_reGVzSwcxUI7ZaOd6v2Rtif5IuwhHXXfhEA4tDZFnx8bw=) [howmet (id 4-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF-sMSGUwyPFZCUZp8KWlkybyk_YaX7LItH3yCRpkz3LCvBbLs3u-V3142DqRndrPganHCJP8y5rX4alUgyK5F5KTwZz2AveWkPzOiTNcOTgekykiLPMnG09Sny5rjAkMqH35YzS7RYR0Wyl7agBLEXvCs933NFJ4ig_y7imboEFk9Tn1ts1_reGVzSwcxUI7ZaOd6v2Rtif5IuwhHXXfhEA4tDZFnx8bw=).
