Why 18/25: The company demonstrates strong, well‑funded R&D and a large patent base focused on fuel‑efficiency and lightweighting—clear indicators of innovation leadership in materials and aerostructures. It’s scored below the absolute leader bracket because most breakthroughs are incremental and applied to core product lines (important and valuable) rather than being disruptive, stand‑alone proprietary climate technologies with industry‑wide commercialization (e.g., large, proprietary low‑carbon power platforms or breakthrough commercial hydrogen systems led entirely by Howmet).

Measurable Impact (17/25) — findings and evidence
- Scope 1 & 2 reductions: Howmet met its near‑term goal (reduce combined Scope 1 & 2 by 21.5% by 2024 vs 2019) — reported 21.7% reduction achieved in 2024. Company commits to a 33.6% absolute reduction of Scope 1 & 2 by 2027 (339,000 tCO2) vs 2019. [howmet (id 2-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECDl0c7V8v-ECp7CBjyghvg5IWiFB1IdNR3IMYtep_iZoctmssbXOqoTvKvAaKWzjbXEs9MSg6peFMnHk4bm3oqQg4UIIyaDZhGNBoVJe20V4s7cu2JChfaKw5qH0Yzg4dJdYDiz1Yd8wfY_eIIdMIFbiDo8m2f-IMZpBpprNu7HWmC5zdWKC86WiX9FukwPKWNVLn9gCcN6z1P3kO3UthqS12-rZtWw=) [howmet (id 2-3)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEgBS7dDo2Ns44QI39ksCwWTkTSJmzgHXafUKvghi51wwor5IXTmiRzGTI1A5L75Nn3RCc7xL-XmeqwWcCEuZXXuDOzFXJMGroii-IoFsQ3ZpAAz9tKwuxuBVda8SxWZgbCa4pmDnNSjTnBxo7jRByTodLc4hJYUOSUAstqyiYsdyPCLlv0xRYP) [howmet (id 1-2)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkmJ70iPFAo6C6ukUbRQJcKKaJ86hoYL3z75KLs-n8rDTZPaqXzaX8dB7PD-ASztY0WvYSDPXM45IYyDf_PeAq9T_zpNpIzsbU3oCYCl-ToxXKHxjGIXXPrf7Q350oRZ2sdeFxPS6TGXQ__eXsTQzvAgE07DA08957CBryx4Tu_dmt-pKGCXz0iw5ddISnpBHQSryow5t04rrMA8d0ED89dtXRMN40eIk=).
- Quantities and intensity improvements: Examples reported include ~95,600 tCO2e avoided from process improvements, energy‑intensity and water‑intensity improvements (water down 16.5% intensity since 2019), hazardous waste intensity improved 23% in 2024, and renewable electricity at 10.6% of supply in 2024. [howmet (id 1-2)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkmJ70iPFAo6C6ukUbRQJcKKaJ86hoYL3z75KLs-n8rDTZPaqXzaX8dB7PD-ASztY0WvYSDPXM45IYyDf_PeAq9T_zpNpIzsbU3oCYCl-ToxXKHxjGIXXPrf7Q350oRZ2sdeFxPS6TGXQ__eXsTQzvAgE07DA08957CBryx4Tu_dmt-pKGCXz0iw5ddISnpBHQSryow5t04rrMA8d0ED89dtXRMN40eIk=) [howmet (id 2-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECDl0c7V8v-ECp7CBjyghvg5IWiFB1IdNR3IMYtep_iZoctmssbXOqoTvKvAaKWzjbXEs9MSg6peFMnHk4bm3oqQg4UIIyaDZhGNBoVJe20V4s7cu2JChfaKw5qH0Yzg4dJdYDiz1Yd8wfY_eIIdMIFbiDo8m2f-IMZpBpprNu7HWmC5zdWKC86WiX9FukwPKWNVLn9gCcN6z1P3kO3UthqS12-rZtWw=).
- Product impacts: Green Concept Wheel (2024) — manufacturing CO2e reduced by ~80% vs standard wheels; lightweighting materials yield fleet fuel efficiency benefits (examples: forged aluminum wheels >10% truck emission reduction; titanium aluminide engine parts raise fuel efficiency ~4–6%). [howmet (id 3-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFC6OfspWZm5G_2blho7AXecH0yFmXSjCZVTB9fY6r3dJJ8k4Uh51PNsXvWlTCR38Y8qo8DZEoxLZUGaS-MFNi1Rnbnu8WT4zyyel2zU2eGSW0HsIBX_7w0D-qA3odTM5bmu-WBkEqlqu4BH1OlboZBH1HW_VGKgziq4mifuQ3cSJd7U0iy19fBZAM69Dle9zuT5VYIUgFneGZYhSUWZrPJR8o8rP7NmQs=) [ainvest (id 1-5)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH0MIcmBEk7Sb-mny7VIMBrPkiAwH2autURUMwzd_inKg85Yz2HPrN8wYp26muavbwwGiUdDmrBo-EZf3l6YGquSK5Nxvqg42_sDBX7watx6T71iA3vfTchCV6ymvCUCHD95p7q0kfvXTcYEz1rAqeXriWgOqXygDrEE943p0eM9XZ0-oKekQ_HveHQ7tMirIws_bjCz2fdc0LG0Pk=) [howmet (id 2-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECDl0c7V8v-ECp7CBjyghvg5IWiFB1IdNR3IMYtep_iZoctmssbXOqoTvKvAaKWzjbXEs9MSg6peFMnHk4bm3oqQg4UIIyaDZhGNBoVJe20V4s7cu2JChfaKw5qH0Yzg4dJdYDiz1Yd8wfY_eIIdMIFbiDo8m2f-IMZpBpprNu7HWmC5zdWKC86WiX9FukwPKWNVLn9gCcN6z1P3kO3UthqS12-rZtWw=).
