- Technology Adoption: 18/25 — Several innovative techs implemented at scale (energy projects, solar, lightweight materials, Green Concept Wheel) but not multiple company‑wide breakthrough climate technologies. [howmet (id 3-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFC6OfspWZm5G_2blho7AXecH0yFmXSjCZVTB9fY6r3dJJ8k4Uh51PNsXvWlTCR38Y8qo8DZEoxLZUGaS-MFNi1Rnbnu8WT4zyyel2zU2eGSW0HsIBX_7w0D-qA3odTM5bmu-WBkEqlqu4BH1OlboZBH1HW_VGKgziq4mifuQ3cSJd7U0iy19fBZAM69Dle9zuT5VYIUgFneGZYhSUWZrPJR8o8rP7NmQs=) [howmet (id 2-0)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECDl0c7V8v-ECp7CBjyghvg5IWiFB1IdNR3IMYtep_iZoctmssbXOqoTvKvAaKWzjbXEs9MSg6peFMnHk4bm3oqQg4UIIyaDZhGNBoVJe20V4s7cu2JChfaKw5qH0Yzg4dJdYDiz1Yd8wfY_eIIdMIFbiDo8m2f-IMZpBpprNu7HWmC5zdWKC86WiX9FukwPKWNVLn9gCcN6z1P3kO3UthqS12-rZtWw=)
- Innovation Leadership: 18/25 — Strong R&D/patents and targeted tech for engines/materials; good partnerships; not yet clearly the industry’s single technology frontrunner across all climate solutions. [howmet (id 4-4)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHKfjN68z_hmnHoN2zC7XF-oLcz5Q9eH9W-2zEUn3XgduPqpfhePC0l0wD0l1-vA7vKc4aaM0APdmTXti792toSrHG3QSdnrZIXOXF55OzRKkIdzNk-iWUzNpAqJvVTfHfqzp8N5RzwR0J4pxeTCZuV9E19TizMe_SB6R7ND9RM2fTJ5DWcRGT9UqShTRfk8w==) [dcfmodeling (id 1-7)](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH4TXulx7BuXg_pycv-cEp4v72iDNIpLvT4C-Nl_oJt2f9hkfmYAnVOklZzJV7szOpnG0bc99BRHAgzBk427ii8TRh2ZxoKf4LjW8zbsUhRuhMSKxDwOQsBQbJWSk0aV0VQ_LZ8m2GMyE_pfR4mJe4xKZw=)
